sequenceDiagram
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>API Server
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant WFC as Workflow Controller<br/>9090/TCP metrics
    participant Pod as Workflow Step Pod
    participant Exec as argoexec<br/>(emissary)
    participant User as User Container
    participant S3 as S3/Minio<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP (optional)

    Note over KFP,K8s: Flow 1: Pipeline Step Execution

    KFP->>K8s: Create Workflow CR<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA Token
    K8s-->>WFC: Workflow event (informer)<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA Token
    WFC->>K8s: Create Step Pod<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA Token
    Note over Pod,Exec: argoexec injected as entrypoint wrapper

    activate Pod
    Exec->>S3: Download input artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, S3 credentials
    S3-->>Exec: Artifact data
    Exec->>User: Execute user command<br/>(process exec, no network)
    User-->>Exec: Exit code + stdout/stderr
    Exec->>S3: Upload output artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, S3 credentials
    Exec->>K8s: Create WorkflowTaskResult CR<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA Token
    deactivate Pod

    WFC->>K8s: Update Workflow status<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA Token

    Note over WFC,DB: Flow 2: Workflow Archival (Optional)

    WFC->>K8s: Watch completed Workflows<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA Token
    K8s-->>WFC: Workflow completion event
    WFC->>DB: Archive workflow data<br/>TCP/5432, Username/Password<br/>Optional SSL

    Note over WFC,S3: Flow 3: Artifact Garbage Collection

    WFC->>K8s: Create WorkflowArtifactGCTask CR<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA Token
    K8s-->>Pod: Schedule GC Pod
    activate Pod
    Pod->>S3: Delete expired artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, Cloud credentials
    Pod->>K8s: Update GCTask status<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA Token
    deactivate Pod
